* REPL

Complete the REPL interface so that it allows top-level special syntax.

* SRFIs

Implement SRFI 206.

* Backends

Support other backends besides Chibi-Scheme.

* Optimization

Do not emit ‘(define-values _... ...)’ in the library and program top-level.

